{"tid":976418,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國麥當勞員工爆料　這「4大地雷餐點」別碰","createTime":"2019-01-10T11:32:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-11T09:13:28.000Z","uid":212399,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9d5c6ccd5a149778ca236992da088e2857099f81","tid":976418,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T11:32:46.000Z","msg":"國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n小心麥當勞也有地雷食物！根據美國網路媒體 「Mashed」整理，美國麥當勞內部員工爆料，有多項餐點「連員工都不吃」，點餐前真的得三思喔！<br />\n報導首先指出的地雷餐點就是「麥克雞塊」，因為員工承認會把放置過久的雞塊拿去重新加熱販售，因為「不管加熱幾次，雞塊吃起來依然還不錯」。也有員工表示，自己絕對不喝「McCaf&eacute;」機器的飲料，因為機器非常難徹底清洗乾淨，都累積著大量噁心的黏稠物，只是消費者不知道罷了。<br />\n主餐部分的地雷，員工透露就是「麥香魚」，因為比較沒有人會點，所以麥香魚常常會久放在加熱區，直到少數客人買走它。最後就是「冰點」部分，被視為地雷餐點的原因跟「McCaf&eacute;」相同，冰品機器不易清洗，所以衛生堪慮。（編輯：吳長諭）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/m/News.aspx?NewsID=483269\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D483269&d=ap59pJTNiO3%2Foi%2FwQdieB6MP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=91847391\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D483269&h=9d134a7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/m/News.aspx?NewsID=483269</a>"},{"pid":"07dcba2243f05f15db9b3374136e1eb873a58ec7","tid":976418,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T11:35:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85961f6a9dba7f77077c0530bd1d69806f479ad1","tid":976418,"uid":150609,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T09:06:50.000Z","msg":"哭了 不敢食了<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SDJDqip.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSDJDqip.gif&h=e3ec5dde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal